snippet.title: Across the River - Complete Walkthrough
snippet.description:
In this video, I play through the Pico-8 game Across the River 100% walkthrough bringing the wolf, the goat, the cabbage, the hunter, the gun, the monkey and the washing machine to the other side for playing game.

If you would like to play the game, visit https://www.lexaloffle.com/bbs/?pid=10838#playing

Benjamin Soulé (C) Across the River
